window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The truth is never what it seems. Neither are the people, regardless of who they are.<br> <br> Mafia romance<br> Age Gap<br> Murder mystery<br> Steamy sex<br> Violence<br> <br> I knew the past would come back to haunt me. It was only a matter of time before my world came crashing down.<br> <br> The only thing I didn’t expect was Mateo. The head of the Italian mafia. We were never meant to cross paths; our worlds vastly different.<br> <br> His green gaze captured me, his touch burning through my defenses. The words he whispered melted away all the years of loneliness. But the secret I kept could get me killed. If he spared me, his rivals wouldn’t. As my secrets unravel, it could cost me everything and everyone I loved.</p> <p><b><i>WARNING: </i></b><i>18+ only. Please listen responsibly. THIS NOVEL CONTAINS TRIGGERING CONTENT.</i></p>"; 
